'''Linguistic Systems, Inc.''', also known as LSI, provides [[language translation]] services (conversion) for all [[Media (communication)|media]] in over 115 languages. LSI focuses on the translation of [[legal]], [[medical]], [[business]], [[institutional]], [[academic]], [[government]] and personal documents. LSI is headquartered in [[Cambridge, Massachusetts]].

==About LSI==

'''Linguistic Systems, Inc. (LSI)''' was founded in 1967 by Martin Roberts and has grown to be one of the largest Total [[Language]] Service Solution Provider companies in the [[United States]].

LSI's translates to/from 115 languages, DTP, [[audio-visual|audio-visual conversions]], [[software localization]], consecutive and simultaneous [[Interpreting|interpreting services]], foreign brand name analysis, and [[machine translation]] with post-editing.

LSI has provided translation services to over half of the [[Fortune 500|Fortune 500 companies]] and most of the [[Fortune 100]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Industries Served|url=http://www.linguist.com/|website=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|publisher=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|accessdate=10 February 2017}}</ref>  Among its clients are [[AT&T]], [[Boeing]], [[Citigroup]], [[Coca-Cola]], [[DuPont]], [[Exxon-Mobil]], [[General Electric]], [[General Motors]], [[Hewlett-Packard]], [[IBM]], [[Johnson & Johnson]], [[Pfizer]], [[Procter & Gamble]], [[Simon & Schuster]], [[Time Warner]], [[Verizon]], and [[Walmart]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Industries: Translation Services Clients|url=http://www.linguist.com/industries-clients.htm|website=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|publisher=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|accessdate=10 February 2017}}</ref>

As of 2013, LSI had a network of more than 7,000 [[translators]] who translate into their native languages{{citation needed|date=February 2017}}. These include highly trained [[lawyers]], [[scientists]], [[engineers]], and other [[bilingual]] professionals.<ref>{{cite web|title=Servives: Overview (Professional Translation Services)|url=http://www.linguist.com/services-overview.htm|website=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|publisher=Linguistic Systems, Inc.|accessdate=10 February 2017}}</ref>

