'''Preis der Stadt Wien für Geisteswissenschaften''' is a prize of the city of [[Vienna]], [[Austria]], awarded annually since 1947 for outstanding contributions in the [[humanities]]. It is worth 8,000 Euros to the winner.{{fact|date=October 2017}}
